Please request pulls with your fancy pony themed desktops.
So that everypony can get inspiration, get cool themes and
perhaps be included in the GNU/Pony project.

But your submission in a uniquely named descriptive directory,
and provide a README.md that displays a previews.

Submissions must include dependencies (do not forget to tell
which distribution you are using), sources for dependencies
if not included in the distribution's offical package positiories;
resource files; and configuration files (or script to set up configurations).

You submission directory should be places in a directory named as
the desktop environment used in the submission.

It is preferable if images are in vector graphics, or in very high
resolution if in raster. Please provide the source files, such as
for example .xfc and .svg files.

